<br />
<br />Yes, but compared to NTSC, it looks really good.
<br />
<br />SECAM should look even better than PAL as AFAIKM their color encoding scheme is even more sophisticated. A major drawback in SECAM is however that SECAM video cannot be easily edited because of it.
<br />
<br />Any good photos of NES/Famiclones connected to PAL TVs?

		

