		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yes, SECAM Famiclone is Dendy. It has two ICs as PPU, they are connected with 8-bit digital bus. Second one is probably a SECAM encoder that uses color number received from PPU. HardWareMan probably know more about this.

		

